        <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Voltages</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono">230 / 460 V</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- WSPX 207 Section -->
  <h2 id="wspx-207">Alfa Laval WSPX 207 TGP — Partial-Discharge <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">Disc-Stack Centrifuge</a></h2>
  <p>
    The Alfa Laval WSPX 207 Centrifuge is a self-cleaning disc-stack centrifuge designed for the three-phase concentration of water-based liquids such as machine coolants and washer liquids.
  </p>
  <p>
    With a <strong>7.5 HP Motor</strong>, the <strong>WSPX 207</strong> centrifuge has a <strong>bowl RPM of 6,400</strong> and can <strong>process 20 GPM</strong> of water-based <strong>machining coolant</strong>.
  </p>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center not-prose">
    <figure class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-auto">
      <img
        src="/images/alfa-laval-mopx-207-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Industrial-Centrifuge-Coolant-600.webp"
        alt="Alfa Laval WSPX-207 Industrial Centrifuge for machining coolant separation and concentration"
        width="600"
        height="360"
        loading="lazy"
        class="rounded-lg w-full md:w-auto md:max-w-sm"
      />
      <figcaption class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Alfa Laval Industrial Centrifuge — Machining Coolant Application</figcaption>
    </figure>
